  25 Apr 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Stable on ia64 wrt bug #175465.

  25 Apr 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64; bug #175465

*xdpyinfo-1.0.2 (31 Mar 2007)

  31 Mar 2007; Joshua Baergen <joshuabaergen@gentoo.org>
  +xdpyinfo-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.  Fixes several memory leaks and other bugs.
  
  I've also added the dga, dmx and xinerama USE-flags per Ingo Bormuth's
  request.  Adding these USE-flags was not possible before this release. (Bug
  #132502)

  10 Oct 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Update description to be less generic.

  01 Oct 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  libXext has a runtime dep on xextproto now, so we don't need to depend on it
  here.

  19 Jul 2006; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Stable on hppa.

  10 Jul 2006; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Mark 1.0.1 stable on ia64

  07 Jul 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.

  01 Jul 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  ppc/sparc/mips/alpha/arm/sh stable

  30 Jun 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64.

  30 Jun 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> xdpyinfo-1.0.1.ebuild:
